{"tid":514284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"從麥當勞雞翼事件睇到香港人骨子裏始終係奴性重","createTime":"2017-12-30T11:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-31T18:17:20.000Z","uid":60665,"like":17,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3487f2506f36859643e0ab6e019c29eb0869ba03","tid":514284,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T11:48:12.000Z","msg":"老老實實，麥當勞畀你換雞槌雞翼係人情，唔畀換係道理<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/513415/page/10\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/513415/page/10</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 1301<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 353<br />\n<br />\n睇下幾多人支持麥當勞新度縮政策？幫麥當勞護航？1301位連登仔支持麥當勞新度縮政策呀<br />\n唔睇下都唔知連登仔大部份都係奴性咁重<br />\n怪唔得泛民咁撚廢，本土又無人支持，保皇又咁橫行啦<br />\n根本大部份連登仔（甚至香港人）骨子裏都係奴性極重，對著間大集團都奶到咁，對著政府實放唔低政府就係權威依種思維"},{"pid":"2425862160635bf2afdfe89ac2b39b025b0fff6a","tid":514284,"uid":85819,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T11:49:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da7d8dd5b68956823513748c4ee8a18e495df49b","tid":514284,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2425862160635bf2afdfe89ac2b39b025b0fff6a","tid":514284,"uid":85819,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T11:49:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T11:51:39.000Z","msg":"吉野家23蚊都有啦"},{"pid":"14fa8130e08a53eca5943a2e7939755f9e37dfc5","tid":514284,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T11:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c8f3988e754b25671036d105fe7b9137b193c9","tid":514284,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T12:02:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed901e2216c941f7ef14166d205e575600b289a","tid":514284,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T12:03:14.000Z"